<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 10:09:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“拉比法”危机表明内塔尼亚胡是多么容易受到极端正统派的勒索</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/crisis-over-rabbis-law-shows-how-vulnerable-netanyahu-is-to-extortion-by-ultra-orthodox/00000190-2f45-d340-a1f8-2f457d190000</link><description>在充满死亡和悲伤的时刻，内塔尼亚胡的联盟正在自杀，因为一项立法的目标是为极端正统政党创造大量就业机会。然而，几名“反叛”利库德集团议员代表了政党选民的强烈情绪，他们再也无法忍受恶心了</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 08:51:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/crisis-over-rabbis-law-shows-how-vulnerable-netanyahu-is-to-extortion-by-ultra-orthodox/00000190-2f45-d340-a1f8-2f457d190000</guid></item><item><title>ADL 因以色列可靠性问题和反犹太主义而面临维基百科禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/adl-faces-wikipedia-ban-over-reliability-concerns-on-israel-antisemitism/00000190-2f1d-d2ff-a5d1-7fdf29a30000</link><description>一位编辑写道，“反诽谤联盟似乎不再遵守反犹太主义的严肃、主流和学术上令人信服的定义”，他要求讨论反犹太主义的请求最终导致了禁令的实施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 07:08:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/adl-faces-wikipedia-ban-over-reliability-concerns-on-israel-antisemitism/00000190-2f1d-d2ff-a5d1-7fdf29a30000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗敦促真主党削弱以色列的核能力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/hurtling-toward-nuclear-capability-iran-urges-hezbollah-to-wear-israel-down/00000190-2cd5-d701-a3d2-7cff0e120000</link><description>以色列情报机构认为，德黑兰对加沙和黎巴嫩战争的进展感到满意，许多伊朗人将其视为击败以色列的长期计划的一部分。随着核能力变得越来越迫在眉睫，人们对总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡如何应对局势的担忧与日俱增</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/hurtling-toward-nuclear-capability-iran-urges-hezbollah-to-wear-israel-down/00000190-2cd5-d701-a3d2-7cff0e120000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷寻求与哈马斯达成人质协议，美国对以色列与真主党的冲突感到担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-frets-over-israel-hezbollah-flare-up-as-jerusalem-seeks-hostage-deal-with-hamas/00000190-2d0e-d2de-af9e-6deed31c0000</link><description>美国高级官员警告以色列北部边境可能爆发全面战争，耶路撒冷表示，未能与哈马斯达成协议可能会加剧局势</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 03:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-frets-over-israel-hezbollah-flare-up-as-jerusalem-seeks-hostage-deal-with-hamas/00000190-2d0e-d2de-af9e-6deed31c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡批评后，美国取消与以色列就伊朗问题举行的战略会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article-live/idf-ten-rockets-launched-from-lebanon-thousands-protest-govt-demand-gaza-deal/00000190-2e48-d39e-a999-7ece6e070000</link><description>在内塔尼亚胡批评拜登政府后，美国取消与以色列就伊朗问题举行的战略会议。 ■ 以色列国防军称，从加沙发射的“空中目标”落在以色列领土的开阔地带。 ■ 以色列国防军：从黎巴嫩发射了 10 枚火箭弹；数千名以色列人抗议政府，要求加沙协议 ■ 内塔尼亚胡猛烈抨击拜登拖延武器；布林肯：美国出于“担忧”审查一批运往以色列的炸弹 ■ 真主党播出无人机镜头，据称显示对以色列海法港的监视</description><pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 02:25:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article-live/idf-ten-rockets-launched-from-lebanon-thousands-protest-govt-demand-gaza-deal/00000190-2e48-d39e-a999-7ece6e070000</guid></item><item><title>面对自己联盟的反对，内塔尼亚胡被迫废除具有分裂性的“拉比法”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/facing-pushback-from-his-own-coalition-netanyahu-forced-to-pull-divisive-rabbis-law/00000190-2da9-d2de-af9e-6deb88460000</link><description>尽管以色列总理从关键小组中驱逐了两名流氓利库德集团成员，但仍无法为新立法赢得多数席位</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 23:30:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-19/ty-article/.premium/facing-pushback-from-his-own-coalition-netanyahu-forced-to-pull-divisive-rabbis-law/00000190-2da9-d2de-af9e-6deb88460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察暴力在与特拉维夫篮球队的最新冲突中从政治蔓延到体育领域</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-violence-spills-from-politics-to-sports-in-latest-clashes-with-tel-aviv-team/00000190-2ca5-d701-a3d2-7caf987a0000</link><description>以色列警方与特拉维夫夏普尔队球迷之间爆发的冲突是警察部队与夏普尔队球迷之间长期紧张关系的一部分，而伊塔马尔·本-格维尔则加剧了这种关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 19:59:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-violence-spills-from-politics-to-sports-in-latest-clashes-with-tel-aviv-team/00000190-2ca5-d701-a3d2-7caf987a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列女队在欧洲游泳锦标赛上夺得以色列首枚金牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-womens-team-wins-israels-first-ever-gold-in-european-swimming-championship/00000190-2bb1-d5f5-a5d6-ebfba4350000</link><description>以色列自由泳接力游泳运动员阿纳斯塔西娅·戈尔本科、达里亚·戈洛瓦蒂、阿亚拉·斯皮茨和莉亚·波隆斯基在欧洲游泳锦标赛上赢得以色列历史上第一枚金牌，男子团体获得第四名</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 19:06:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-womens-team-wins-israels-first-ever-gold-in-european-swimming-championship/00000190-2bb1-d5f5-a5d6-ebfba4350000</guid></item><item><title>真主党播出无人机镜头，据称显示对以色列海法港和以色列国防军海军基地的监视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-airs-drone-footage-allegedly-showing-surveillance-of-haifa-port-idf-navy-base/00000190-2c03-d2ff-a5d1-7ccf791c0000</link><description>除了以色列海军在海法港口的主要基地外，真主党还声称拍摄了海法的安全设施；以色列外长威胁对真主党和黎巴嫩发动“全面”战争</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 18:37:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-airs-drone-footage-allegedly-showing-surveillance-of-haifa-port-idf-navy-base/00000190-2c03-d2ff-a5d1-7ccf791c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡攻击拜登：阻止向以色列运送武器是“不可思议的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-attacks-biden-inconceivable-to-hold-back-arms-shipments-to-israel/00000190-2c13-db38-adff-fcb344ab0000</link><description>当被问及这批武器运输的状况时，美国国务卿表示，这批重载炸弹仍在接受审查，但“其他一切进展正常”；白宫表示：“我们不知道他在说什么”</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 17:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-attacks-biden-inconceivable-to-hold-back-arms-shipments-to-israel/00000190-2c13-db38-adff-fcb344ab0000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼以色列向加沙和黎巴嫩扩张的幻想将杀死我们所有人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-18/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-far-rights-fantasies-about-expansion-into-gaza-lebanon-will-kill-us-all/00000190-2c0a-d5f5-a5d6-edea5b220000</link><description>以色列极右翼领导人表示支持将以色列边界扩展到新领土，而他们甚至无法保护目前家园中的平民，他们非常清楚地表明，通过努力寻求政治解决方案来维持以色列人的生存或确保未来是不可行的。在他们的名单上</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 17:01:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-18/ty-article/.highlight/israeli-far-rights-fantasies-about-expansion-into-gaza-lebanon-will-kill-us-all/00000190-2c0a-d5f5-a5d6-edea5b220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 256 天：本格维尔表示他致力于在加沙定居</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-256-ben-gvir-says-hes-committed-to-settling-in-gaza/00000190-2c40-d39e-a999-7eceae4c0001</link><description>真主党发布了以色列海军基地的航拍镜头，声称该镜头是由未被以色列拦截的无人机拍摄的。 ■ 极右翼部长本-格维尔表示，他致力于“在整个加沙”建设犹太人定居点。以色列此前被他们封锁了数月 ■ 战争进入 256 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 16:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-256-ben-gvir-says-hes-committed-to-settling-in-gaza/00000190-2c40-d39e-a999-7eceae4c0001</guid></item><item><title>被排除在外：随着加沙地区危机的加剧，埃尔多安和土耳其被边缘化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/erdogan-and-turkey-have-been-sidelined-in-the-gaza-based-regional-crisis/00000190-2b6f-dafe-a3d6-3f6f30ee0000</link><description>在土耳其总统抨击以色列和拜登政府的同时，他也试图保护自己国家的利益，例如与以色列盟友阿塞拜疆的经济关系。不管怎样，“第二天”的会谈中没有他的座位</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:25:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/turkey/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/erdogan-and-turkey-have-been-sidelined-in-the-gaza-based-regional-crisis/00000190-2b6f-dafe-a3d6-3f6f30ee0000</guid></item><item><title>“黎巴嫩，应许之地的一部分”：以色列救世主右翼瞄准新的定居点领土</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-part-of-the-promised-land-israels-messianic-right-wing-targets-new-territory/00000190-2b9d-d340-a1f8-2b9d18220000</link><description>在你对周一举行小型在线会议、着眼于夺回“上帝应许之地”的宗教弥赛亚主义者不屑一顾之前，请记住，他们的约旦河西岸定居点计划在 50 年前似乎同样古怪</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:19:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-part-of-the-promised-land-israels-messianic-right-wing-targets-new-territory/00000190-2b9d-d340-a1f8-2b9d18220000</guid></item><item><title>报告：新证据显示以色列国防军事先详细了解哈马斯袭击以色列的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/report-new-evidence-reveals-idf-had-detailed-prior-knowledge-of-hamas-plan-to-raid-israel/00000190-2afb-d2de-af9e-6ffbdf700000</link><description>一份前所未见的以色列国防军文件揭示了哈马斯入侵以色列行动计划的令人震惊的新细节；报告概述哈马斯下令劫持 200 至 250 名以色列人作为人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 14:53:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/report-new-evidence-reveals-idf-had-detailed-prior-knowledge-of-hamas-plan-to-raid-israel/00000190-2afb-d2de-af9e-6ffbdf700000</guid></item><item><title>由于分裂法案令内塔尼亚胡联盟感到不安，利库德集团将流氓MK从关键委员会中驱逐出去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/mks-mayors-spar-over-contentious-bill-giving-govt-control-of-city-rabbi-appointments/00000190-2b82-d39e-a999-7fce7a3d0000</link><description>以色列利库德集团主席将两名议员从议会委员会中除名，因为他们反对极端正统的沙斯党提出的赋予政府任命城市拉比权力的立法</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 14:39:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/mks-mayors-spar-over-contentious-bill-giving-govt-control-of-city-rabbi-appointments/00000190-2b82-d39e-a999-7fce7a3d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察加大对示威者的镇压，以色列议员称反政府抗议者是“哈马斯的手臂”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/mk-calls-anti-govt-protesters-arm-of-hamas-as-police-crackdown-on-protests-intensifies/00000190-2ae2-d95e-a3ff-eef60c280000</link><description>在内塔尼亚胡总理耶路撒冷官邸外举行的示威活动中，三名反政府抗议者受伤，九人被捕。利库德集团议员尼西姆·瓦图里后来澄清了他的声明，称他对自己的言论感到“震惊”</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:45:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/mk-calls-anti-govt-protesters-arm-of-hamas-as-police-crackdown-on-protests-intensifies/00000190-2ae2-d95e-a3ff-eef60c280000</guid></item><item><title>现在是参观以色列戈兰高地的最佳时机（忽略真主党的火箭弹）</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-06-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hezbollah-is-throwing-rockets-but-golan-heights-locals-think-you-should-still-vacate-here/00000190-217b-d4b4-a7d6-e9fb431e0000</link><description>以旅游业为生的戈兰高地居民恳求以色列人回来参观，并承诺这里一如既往的安全</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:10:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-06-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hezbollah-is-throwing-rockets-but-golan-heights-locals-think-you-should-still-vacate-here/00000190-217b-d4b4-a7d6-e9fb431e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵命令巴勒斯坦未成年人处理他藏在祖父家的爆炸物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-order-palestinian-minor-to-handle-explosives-he-had-hidden/00000190-2a38-d5f5-a5d6-ebfa0b1e0000</link><description>本月早些时候，这名巴勒斯坦少年在带领以色列军队制造炸弹后在盖勒吉利耶被捕。以色列国防军上传的视频显示，这名青少年正在清除屋外的爆炸物，以色列国防军消息人士称这没有问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 10:49:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-order-palestinian-minor-to-handle-explosives-he-had-hidden/00000190-2a38-d5f5-a5d6-ebfa0b1e0000</guid></item><item><title>报告：内塔尼亚胡问警方为什么“没有一个激进犹太人”因杀害巴勒斯坦人而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-police-why-not-single-radical-jew-arrested-in-killing-of-palestinians/00000190-29f6-d340-a1f8-29f613450000</link><description>在一份披露的录音中，以色列安全官员在会议期间发生争吵，而内塔尼亚胡在美国的压力下敦促采取行动打击定居者的暴力行为</description><pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 10:27:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-asks-police-why-not-single-radical-jew-arrested-in-killing-of-palestinians/00000190-29f6-d340-a1f8-29f613450000</guid></item></channel></rss>